name: Leica lens style
description:
基于LEICA SUMMILUX镜头所拍摄照片训练的真实性风格。体现出徕卡镜头所拥有的景深、色彩、光斑、对比度等特性。适用于具有高度真实性的人物摄影照片。

触发词：leica_style,

描述扩展：Depth of Field, Bokeh,

权重可以设置高一些。

Authentic style trained on photos taken with LEICA SUMMILUX lenses. It reflects the depth of field, color,Bokeh, contrast and other characteristics of Leica lenses. Ideal for photographs of people with a high degree of realism.

Trigger words: leica_style,

Description extensions: Depth of Field, Bokeh,

The weight can be set higher.
